Package KioskApp.Inventory

Class Item

java.lang.Object
KioskApp.Inventory.Item
Direct Known Subclasses:
BakeryItem, DairyItem, FrozenItem, MiscItem, PantryItem, ProduceItem
public class Item extends Object
Class of items to be used for items in grocery stores. Contains several variables relating to grocery store items like name, department, price, and barcode. Cotains several overloaded constructors as well as methods to set and get variables.
